\det(I+\lambda A) = \exp[ \text{tr} \log (I+ \lambda A)] = \exp[ \text{tr} ( \lambda A + \mathcal{O}(\lambda^2) )] = 1 + \lambda \,\text{tr} A + \mathcal{O}(\lambda^2).
